Our core purpose is maximizing stakeholder value by being responsive to market needs as the preferred provider of bio-based products from renewable sources produced in a safe efficient working environment.
Mercer is one of the world's largest producers of NBSK market pulp and has become a leader among forest products companies in embracing the economy and maximizing the value of our forest resources. Our large-scale, modern mills produce not only NBSK pulp, but also biomass-based green energy and chemicals  With our successful acquisition of one of Germany’s largest sawmills near Friesau, Germany in April 2017, we launched Mercer Timber Products, our entry into the softwood lumber sector. 














