Mercer Timber Products




























Precision in Quality and Service
The trusted choice in sustainable, quality wood products
Contact Us



Mercer Timber Products produces a wide range of high-quality softwood lumber products, leveraging local sourcing and sustainable best practices, to efficiently and productively serve the diverse needs of our customers around the world. We aspire to produce the highest quality lumber using only wood from sustainably managed forests in order to preserve our natural resources and support a sound environment.
Mercer Timber Products is a subsidiary of Mercer International Inc., one of the largest producers of Northern Bleached Softwood Kraft pulp in the world. Mercer Timber Products was established with the acquisition of one of Germany’s largest sawmills near Friesau, Germany in April 2017.

Fast Facts




1.3 million m3(550 million board feet)production capacity



Approximately 13MW ofelectricity and 49.5MW of thermalenergy production capacity



300 experienced professionalscurrently employed





Careers



Mercer Timber Products values the growth of our employees. With a strong track record of successful project execution, we dedicate substantial resources to training and developing the right candidates for our team. To learn more about career opportunities, you can email us at info@mercertimber.de. We look forward to welcoming you to the Mercer family!
